  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 160 degrees Celsius.",
    "In a large mixing bowl, whisk together yeast, flour, and buttermilk.",
    "Add the Grana Padano cheese, eggs, olive oil, allspice, cumin, salt, and black pepper to the bowl and mix until well combined.",
    "Add the chopped onions, garlic, and labneh cheese to the bowl and mix until smooth.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a 24cm round baking dish.",
    "Drizzle the clarified butter and ghee over the top of the mixture.",
    "Bake in the preheated oven for 45 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Remove from the oven and drizzle with pomegranate molasses.",
    "Sprinkle with chopped fresh parsley, dates, and a pinch of cayenne pepper.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy!",
    "Garnish with a dollop of tahini and a sprinkle of sumac, if desired."
  ],
